    "uen": "202007906Z",
    "description": "<p>Confirm Good is a Singapore-based media publishing platform that brings the latest deals, news and happenings to locals in our little red dot.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We offer first-hand information on deals and promotions on a daily basis and we curate and pick out the best deals for our subscribers. We are the first Telegram channel in Singapore to have exclusive partnerships with well-loved brands such as Krispy Kreme, Llao Llao, LiHO, and Tiger Sugar to offer our subscribers giveaways, one-for-one deals, and many other promotions and discounts!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are expanding to bring our tight-knit community even closer by adding a more personal touch to our offerings through Confirm Good with not only a wider variety of partnerships, but also with articles covering various topics to appeal to a wider demographic.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>With well-researched insights and advice spanning a wide range of topics, we seek to deliver simple to understand and beneficial contents for our readers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are always on a lookout for talents and we can offer you a broad range of exciting careers of your choice.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To qualify for a full-time position with us, we would prefer it if you have at least 2 years of working experience in a relevant field or if you can impress us with your work.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you are really keen to try your hand at something new and don’t have the experience, you can apply for our 6-month Internship Program.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We look forward to hearing from you :)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Don’t worry, Confirm Good&nbsp;<em>Lah!</em></p>",
